Amisulpride is also used as an antiemetic agent. In the US, the intravenous formulation of amisulpride is used to treat and prevent postoperative nausea and vomiting in adults, either as monotherapy or in combination with another antiemetic agent of a different drug class.[L32759] It is marketed under the brand name Barhemsys.', '["N05AL05"]', '[]');
